('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000001','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000001',5,'Esperienza indimenticabile!','Il personale era eccezionale e la vista dal balcone mozzafiato. Colazione inclusa di altissimo livello. Torneremo sicuramente.',18,true,now()-INTERVAL '12 days',now()-INTERVAL '12 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000002','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000002',4,'Great stay, minor noise issue','Beautiful hotel in an amazing location. Room was spacious and clean. Street noise at night was the only downside.',12,true,now()-INTERVAL '25 days',now()-INTERVAL '25 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000003','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000003',5,'Best hotel in the city','From check-in to checkout, everything was flawless. The rooftop bar alone is worth the stay. Staff anticipated our every need.',28,true,now()-INTERVAL '5 days',now()-INTERVAL '5 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000004','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000004',3,'Carino ma troppo caro','Camera pulita e posizione buona, ma il rapporto qualita-prezzo non e dei migliori. Colazione discreta.',4,true,now()-INTERVAL '45 days',now()-INTERVAL '45 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000005','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000005',4,'Lovely boutique experience','Charming property with lots of character. The courtyard garden is magical. Rooms are cozy if a bit compact.',15,true,now()-INTERVAL '30 days',now()-INTERVAL '30 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000006','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000006',5,'Perfetto per la luna di miele','Abbiamo scelto questo hotel per il nostro anniversario e non potevamo fare scelta migliore. Romantico, elegante, curato nei dettagli.',22,true,now()-INTERVAL '8 days',now()-INTERVAL '8 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000007','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000007',2,'Disappointing for the price','Expected much more given the star rating. AC was unreliable, breakfast buffet underwhelming. Location saves it from a 1-star.',3,true,now()-INTERVAL '60 days',now()-INTERVAL '60 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000008','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000008',4,'Ottimo rapporto qualita-prezzo','Hotel moderno con camere spaziose. Piscina sul tetto fantastica. Personale gentile e disponibile.',10,true,now()-INTERVAL '18 days',now()-INTERVAL '18 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000009','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000009',5,'A hidden gem','We almost booked elsewhere but so glad we found this place. Quiet, beautiful, and the breakfast spread is incredible.',25,true,now()-INTERVAL '3 days',now()-INTERVAL '3 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000010','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000010',4,'Solid choice for families','Kids loved the pool and play area. Rooms are large enough for a family of four. Restaurant on-site is convenient.',8,true,now()-INTERVAL '40 days',now()-INTERVAL '40 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000011','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000011',3,'Nella media','Non male, ma niente di speciale. La posizione e comoda per visitare il centro. Bagno un po piccolo.',2,true,now()-INTERVAL '55 days',now()-INTERVAL '55 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000012','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000012',5,'Exceeded all expectations','The concierge arranged a private tour that made our trip. Every detail of this hotel shows they care about guests.',30,true,now()-INTERVAL '7 days',now()-INTERVAL '7 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000013','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000013',4,'Very comfortable stay','Modern amenities, fast WiFi, great shower pressure. The gym is well-equipped. Would happily stay again on business.',6,true,now()-INTERVAL '22 days',now()-INTERVAL '22 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000014','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000014',2,'Servizio deludente','Check-in lentissimo, camera non pronta nonostante arrivo nel pomeriggio. Peccato perche la struttura in se sarebbe bella.',1,false,now()-INTERVAL '70 days',now()-INTERVAL '70 days'),
('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000015','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000015',5,'World-class luxury','If you want to treat yourself, this is the place. The spa alone is worth the visit. Michelin-level dining on site.',20,true,now()-INTERVAL '15 days',now()-INTERVAL '15 days'),
