('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000009','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000024',4,'Great pool and spa','Spent most of our time at the pool area which is gorgeous. Room was comfortable. Restaurant pricey but good.',13,true,now()-INTERVAL '20 days',now()-INTERVAL '20 days'),
