('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000012','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000027',4,'Perfect for a weekend getaway','Two nights here felt like a mini vacation. Loved the terrace bar and the complimentary aperitivo.',14,true,now()-INTERVAL '16 days',now()-INTERVAL '16 days'),
