('f0000010-0000-0000-0000-000000000030','HOTEL','c0000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000055',4,'Pleasantly surprised','Did not expect much at this price point but the room was modern, bed was great, and breakfast had real espresso.',10,true,now()-INTERVAL '34 days',now()-INTERVAL '34 days'),
